rds That Endure </div><div class="t m867 x27 h33 y6e8 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MEMORY VERSE: </div><div class="t m23dc x19 h2b y3ee ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Henceforth there is laid up for me a crown of righteousness, </div><div class="t m11ec x5d h2b y283 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">which the Lord, the righteous Judge, shall give me at that day: and not to me </div><div class="t m20c4 x5d h2b y847 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">only, but unto all them also that love His appearing.&quot; 2 Tim. 4:8. </div><div class="t m488 x27 h33 y5 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">STUDY HELPS: </div><div class="t m1975 xa h2b y5 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Testimonies,&quot; Vol. 6, pages 305-312; &quot;S.D.A. Bible Commentary.&quot; </div><div class="t m313 x27 h33 y1f5 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">STUDY AIM: </div><div class="t m12b1 x35 h2b ya57 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">To gain a new vision of the part God&apos;s children are to play in the </div><div class="t ma5c x5d h2b y501 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">successful completion of the church&apos;s mission. </div><div class="t mbd9 x27 h33 y9 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lesson Outline: </div><div class="t ma8f x27 h33 y157 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Introduction </div><div class="t m79 x27 h33 y5ed ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I. Stewards of an Organized Work </div><div class="t m988 x73 h4 y28b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m5c3 x4e h4 y28b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s work to be done with decency </div><div class="t ma2 x4e h4 y16 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and order. 1 Cor. 14:40. </div><div class="t m127 x73 h4 y408 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m5f0 x4e h4 y94 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Why Christ ordained the twelve </div><div class="t md0c x4e h4 y4ce ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">disciples. Mark 3:14. </div><div class="t m2b6 x73 h4 y40a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m4ce x4e h4 y1fd ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The great commission. </div><div class="t m3d5 x4e h4 y58a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc